notes: [Added] Ability to add custom subject line from submited form
[Added] You can now add custom From Name to your notifications (for form submitter)
[Fixed] Fixed file uploads and email attachments
[Improved] Added ability to rename uploaded files on the entry page
[Improved] Added ability to use Sprout Fields within your forms
[Added] Submission data can now be passed to custom routes
[Fixed] richfield input can now display validation message if set to required
[Added] Added ability to rename plugin name in sidebar
[Added] Added ability to allow/disallow non-admin users to add/edit/delete forms and entries
